<textList name="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_MANTIS_HIVE">	
	<text>If you thought Mantis were deadly in other sectors, nothing can match the rage of a Mantis when you've entered their territory.</text>	
	<text>Hive Mantis aren't very friendly, but now that you've invaded their hive they'll stop at nothing to destroy your ship. A furious Mantis ship spots you and attacks.</text>	
	<text>You're hailed by a Mantis ship. "Federation fleshsack? Here in Hive? You have death wish. Let me grant it!"</text>	
	<text>You're greeted by the sight of a Mantis ship scavenging the remains of the last poor ship to have intruded on the Hive. Their attacker moves in to make you the next example.</text>	
	<text>You receive a hail from the Mantis ship at this beacon. "You come to Hive, so you must understand that you shall not leave Hive!"</text>	
	<text>A Mantis ship moves in to attack, set on the defending the Hive from your ship.</text>	
	<text>It doesn't take long for the Mantis ship here to notice you. They hail you. "Federation not welcome in Hive! You know this, yet you come here. Prepare die."</text>	
		
	<text>Something red looms. It's the Mantis.</text> <!--this one HAD to be included-->	
</textList>	


