<textList name="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_SUZERAIN">	
	<text>Suzerains are no force to be reckoned with. Unfortunately this beacon currently hosts a Suzerain, and they seem eager to reckon with you.</text>	
	<text>A Suzerain ship approaches, ready to attack! You hurry to arm the guns.</text>	
	<text>Suzerains are chosen and trained by the Mantis Bishops to be the strongest warriors in the galaxy. Unfortunately for you, at this beacon you find yourself squared off against one of the Suzerain's ships.</text>	
	<text>At the first sight of the cyan hull, you know the ship at this beacon is a Suzerain. You prepare yourself for a fight.</text>	
	<text>Suzerains utilize both drone and boarding tech to kill their enemies. You find yourself face to face with a Suzerain ship and have no choice but to fight.</text>	
	<text>You're hailed by a Suzerain warrior aboard the nearby ship. "Ah, Federation ship. You are first kill I make since I become Suzerain! I thank you, and welcome you to death."</text>	
