	</beaconType>
	<text>This is it- the Mantis Hive. No wonder it's so hard to find, as the bulk of the city is located in a massive cavern underground. Thermal power plants are scattered around massive pits of magma and a large city stands in the center. Even from such a distance, you can see the royal palace...</text>
